Possible commands: 

 help -- Display Help Text
water -- Water plants (today)
water_location -- Water all plants in location (today)
fertilize -- Fertilize plants (today)
rain -- It rained (all outside plants will be watered)
new_growth -- Enter new growth
new_plant -- Enter new plant
new_species -- Enter new species
new_activity -- Enter new activity
update_species -- Update species
update_plant -- Update plant
today -- Enter the current date as input
move_to_graveyard -- Move Plant to graveyard
abort -- Abort the current action
push -- Push local changes to github
check_logs -- Check warnings generated from build
exit -- Exit the bot
